message: Hello Bob, thank you for your interest in our product. Based on its exceptional quality and value, I'm offering it at $2000000. I believe this price reflects both its unique characteristics and the value it can bring. I look forward to hearing your thoughts on this offer.

Thank you, Alice, for the offer. I appreciate the quality and value of your product, but I have budget constraints. I'm willing to offer $600000 for it, considering it's above my alternative option, but still within my budget.
